-- B/E Aerospace says exploring possible sale or merger
-- By Scott DiSavino
-- Sun May 04, 2014 12:20PM EDT
-- None



May 4 (Reuters) - B/E Aerospace <BEAV.O>, a maker of aircraft cabin interior  products, said on Sunday it is exploring strategic alternatives including a possible sale or merger of the company.

In addition, the company said in a statement it had postponed its May 5 investor meeting.